title: Ep. 242 – Zer0 (inches) Books
description: Doug Lain of Zer0 Books  joins us to pitch his youtube channel which has community strikes against it, and I twist his arm into making it about big tech censorship. he's not a fascist or glenn greenwald so you're not allowed to get mad about it.
